author: RTÉ News
title: 'No evidence' that Covid-19 transmitted on packaging
description: There is no evidence to show that Covid-19 can be transmitted via food or food packaging, according to Safefood.
content:
There is no evidence to show that Covid-19 can be transmitted via food or food packaging, according to Safefood.
